 * Returns whether the fade-in has completed.
 *
 * @param {OpenSeadragon.TiledImage} tiledImage
 * @param {OpenSeadragon.Tile} tile
 * @param {Number} x
 * @param {Number} y
 * @param {Number} level
 * @param {Number} levelOpacity
 * @param {Number} currentTime
 * @returns {Boolean}
